doctype html
head
  meta(http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
  // So that mobile will display zoomed in
  meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge')
  // enable media queries for windows phone 8
  meta(name='format-detection' content='date=no')
  // disable auto date linking in iOS 7-9
  meta(name='format-detection' content='telephone=no')
  // disable auto telephone linking in iOS 7-9
  title User sign-up
// 100% background wrapper (grey background)
table(border='0' width='100%' height='100%' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' bgcolor='#F0F0F0')
  tr
    td(align='center' valign='top' bgcolor='#F0F0F0' style='background-color: #F0F0F0;')
      // 600px container (white background)
      table.container(border='0' width='600' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' style='font-family: sans-serif;width:600px;max-width:600px')
        tr
          td.container-padding.header(align='center' style='padding:15px; justify-content:center;align-items:center' bgcolor='#3E82B0')
            img(src=appUrl+"/app/assets/logo-white.png" style='width: 60px;height: auto;object-fit: cover;')
            h3(style='margin:0; padding:0; color: #ffffff;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 10px;font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500;') %recipient.appName%
        tr
          td.content(align='left' style='font-family: sans-serif;padding-top:12px;padding-bottom:0px;background-color:#ffffff')
            table.force-row(width='600' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' style='width: 600px;')
              tr
                td.content-wrapper(style='padding-left:24px;padding-right:24px')
                  .title(style='font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:#585858;line-height: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;')
                    br
                    strong(style='display: flex ;color: #333; align-item:center;font-size: 18px;')
                        | Hello &nbsp; 
                        nbsp
                          h4(style='margin: 0; text-transform: capitalize') %recipient.storeName%,
                    br
                    |  Recently you have installed our app(Announcement Bar with Slider) and then uninstalled it. I would like to tell you that we are working hard to improve our app and providing the best service to our users.
                    br
                    br
                    |  We have fixed bugs and also added new features like...
                    br
                    br
                    strong 1. Work with fixed header Store
                    br
                    strong 2. Countdown Timer
                    br  
                    strong 3. Auto responsive
                    br  
                    strong 4. Page wise Different Announcement
                    br
                    strong 5. 20+ In/out Animations
                    br
                    br
                    |  Can you spare two minutes for feedback? we would like the opportunity to resolve your issue and make the best out of it. 
                    br
                    |  Here is link of our new updated app 
                    br
                    
                    br
                    a(style='background:rgb(62, 130, 176);color:white;text-align:center;padding:10px 15px;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;', class='button', href='https://apps.shopify.com/announcement-bar-with-slider') Install App
                    
              tr
                td.content-wrapper(style='padding-left:24px;padding-right:24px')
                  div(style='color: #757575;font-size: 14px;font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 30px')
                    br
                    |  Have a Nice Day! 
                    br
                    |  Friends at %recipient.appName%
